html
	head
		include includes/header.pug
	body
		h2= message
		H3 Welcome, #{currentUser.username}
		p 
			| Here you can view and edit your information. To see how other members view your profile, click here 
			strong (en dat moet dan dus nog een link worden naar de public profile page)
		br
		

		h4 Profile details that can not be changed
		

		p Your username: #{currentUser.username}
		p Your team: you are a #{currentUser.kindOfPerson}
		p Your current score: #{currentUser.score}
		p
			| (Get a higher score by 
			a(href='goaloverview') completing more goals
			| )
		

		p Your finished goals:
		em EN DAN HIER EEN LIJST MET VOLTOOIDE OPDRACHTEN MET EEN LINK ERNAAR?
		br


		h4 Profile details that can be changed


		p Your current profile picture:
		p 
			em SOMEHOW PICTURE HERE, standaard van een kat of hond ( "if currentuser.kindofperson == cat, then"etc)
		p (Change)
		br


		p Your bio: #{currentUser.bio}
		form(action='/profile' method='post' autocomplete='off')
			input(name='newbio' type='text' placeholder='change your bio' required)
			input(type='submit' value='change bio' id='submitnewbio')
		br


		p Your date of birth: #{currentUser.dob}
		p (change date of birth)
		form(action='/profile' method='post' autocomplete='off')
			input(name='newdob' type='date' required)
			input(type='submit' value='change date of birth' id='submitnewdob')
		br


		p Your email address: #{currentUser.email}
		p Change e-mail:
		form(action='/profile' method='post' autocomplete='off')
			input(name='newemail' type='email' placeholder='yournew@emailadres.com' required)
			input(type='submit' value='change e-mail' id='submitnewemail')
		br


		p To change your password, first please add your old password.
		p invulveld oud wachtwoord
		p invulveld nieuw wachtwoord
		p invulveld nieuw wachtwoord (ter controle)
		br


		h4 I want to delete my profile
		p Are you sure? We'd hate to see you go!
		p This action is irreversible.
		p We require your password before confirmation
		p invulveld wachtwoord
		p knop DELETE


		h4 LOGOUT knop nog naar navbar verplaatsen, zodat een gebruiker niet per ongeluk op verwijder drukt ipv logout
		a(href='logout') Log-out


